  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. The total bill was $25.00. The percentage 20% is equivalent to the decimal 0.2. The tip is the product of the percentage and the total bill; therefore, <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"0 point 2 times 25, equals 5\"></span>, so the tip was $5.00.<p>Choices A, B, and C are incorrect and may be the result of incorrectly converting the given percentage or a calculation error.</p></p>\n",
